OL,3,CJersey children more vulnerable to
OL,4,Charm online, report finds
OL,6,FDescribing the excessive use of
OL,7,Fscreens as a "public health crisis",
OL,8,Fthe report argues that the island must
OL,9,Fimmediately develop a "coordinated,
OL,10,Ffuture-facing strategy" to better
OL,11,Fprotect children against online harms.
OL,13,FThe panel's findings come after
OL,14,FJersey, unlike Guernsey, chose not to
OL,15,Fadopt the UK's Online Safety Act in
OL,16,F2023.
