OL,4,Charm online, report finds
OL,6,FTheir key recommendations include:
OL,8,FThe chair of the CEHA Scrutiny Panel,
OL,9,FDeputy Catherine Curtis, says her
OL,10,Fbiggest concern is that "there is no
OL,11,Fspecific legislation to protect
OL,12,Fchildren online in Jersey".
OL,14,F"There are some laws that can be
OL,15,Fupdated to help with this, and some
OL,16,Fnew laws coming into place that will
OL,17,Fcover some of the issues - but that
OL,18,Fwill still leave huge gaps", she
OL,19,Fexplains.
