OL,6,FJersey banned the use of smartphones
OL,7,Fin schools from the start of this
OL,8,Facademic year.
OL,10,FIn response to the CEHA Panel's
OL,11,Ffindings, a Government statement
OL,12,Facknowledged "the need for Jersey's
OL,13,Flegislative, regulatory and policy
OL,14,Fframeworks to be robust, responsive,
OL,15,Fand aligned with best practice in
OL,16,Fsafeguarding children and young people
OL,17,Fin the digital environment".
