OL,3,CJersey children more vulnerable to
OL,4,Charm online, report finds
OL,6,F"Online safety requires education and
OL,7,Faction in all parts of our community
OL,8,Fand there have been a number of
OL,9,Fimportant gobernment-led initiatives
OL,10,Fin this area," Deputy Moz Scott,
OL,11,FAssistant Minister for Sustainable
OL,12,FEconomic Development, explains.
OL,14,F"This includes legislation to support
OL,15,Fonline privacy and the removal of
OL,16,Fillegal content.
OL,18,F"This work is well underway and we
OL,19,Fwill be launching a public
OL,20,Fconsultation on the draft legislation
OL,21,Fshortly."
